<p><a href="#sdfootnote5anc" name="sdfootnote5sym">5</a>Alexander Doty, <em>Whose Text is it Anyway? Queer Studies, Queer Auteurs and Queer Authorship</em>, w: <em>Queer Cinema...</em>, s. 20.</p>
<p><a href="#sdfootnote6anc" name="sdfootnote6sym">6</a>Judith Halberstam, <em>The Queer Art of Failure</em>, Duke University Press, Durnham-London 2011.</p>
<p><a href="#sdfootnote7anc" name="sdfootnote7sym">7</a>Ibidem, s. 7.</p>
<p><a href="#sdfootnote8anc" name="sdfootnote8sym">8</a>Halberstam przytacza ten cytat za autobiografią Crispa: <em>The Naked Civil Servant </em>(1975, reż. Jack Gold). Zob. Halberstam, <em>The Queer Art of Failure</em>, s. 87.</p>
<p><a href="#sdfootnote9anc" name="sdfootnote9sym">9</a>Ibidem, s. 12.</p>
<p><a href="#sdfootnote10anc" name="sdfootnote10sym">10</a>Ibidem, s. 20.</p>
